# 🔄 Kansas Frontier Matrix — **Hazards Transformation Layer**  
`data/work/tmp/hazards/transforms/`

**Mission:** Reproject, harmonize, and CF-compliance–validate all hazard datasets (tornado, flood, wildfire, drought) to achieve spatial consistency, temporal alignment, and reproducible provenance under FAIR+CARE and ISO standards.

