## 🧠 Transformation Workflow Overview
```mermaid
flowchart TD
A[Hazard Datasets (staging/)] --> B[CF Metadata Validation + CRS Audit]
B --> C[Reprojection → EPSG:4326]
C --> D[Spatial Resampling + COG Generation]
D --> E[Checksum + FAIR+CARE Validation]
E --> F[Governance Ledger Registration]
```

