## 🧬 CF Metadata Alignment Policy
- All datasets must include **global attributes**: `title`, `institution`, `source`, `history`, `references`, `license`.  
- **Variables** standardized via **CF names** and SI units.  
- All coordinate axes labeled and dimensioned properly (`lat`, `lon`, `time`).  
- **Metadata fixes** logged in `cf_fix_logs.json` with timestamps and responsible user.

